title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 22 2022

description:
After Biden catches covid, the White House concedes everyone will get it and contact tracing "Doesn't matter." Covid will be a seasonal pandemic, people will see the pandemic as part of modern life, not a public health emergency. No matter who the GOP candidate will be, the media will say "worse than Hitler." DeSantis is the only candidate who can go toe-to-toe with Trump. Buck wants to adopt a pet red fox. Clay warns about dating girls with multiple pet snakes. Pennsylvania police shoot and kill 15-foot-long pet snake that was strangling man's neck.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
